Hi John,
It would be correct for a 1966-67 VW.  The Sapphire IV AM/FM would be for the 
same era.  Though the knobs are for a type 3, the bus and bug ones match the 
black rubber knobs of the dash and are a PITA to find due to being a one year 
knob.
